longBusinessSummary: 1ST SUMMIT BANCORP of Johnstown, Inc. operates as the bank holding company for 1ST SUMMIT BANK that provides various banking products and services. It accepts various deposits, such as checking, statement savings, interest-bearing and noninterest-bearing demand deposit, money market, time, and individual retirement accounts, as well as certificates of deposit. The company also offers residential real estate, commercial mortgage, commercial, and consumer loans; wealth management, investment, and trust services; credit and debit cards; and life insurance products. The company was formerly known as SUMMIT Bancorp, Inc. and changed its name to 1ST SUMMIT BANCORP of Johnstown, Inc. in 1996. 1ST SUMMIT BANCORP of Johnstown, Inc. was incorporated in 1924 and is based in Johnstown, Pennsylvania.
